    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_aoi_01_01/sud_vo_adv_bond_aoi_01_01-ai001.m4a",
      "text": "葵さん、お疲れ様です！\n……え？　お昼休みなのにダンスの練習ですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thank you for your effort‚ Aoi-san!\n…Huh? Dance practice during lunch break?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 5.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolyard-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolyard-00-noon",
      "startTime": 12.000000763
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_aoi_01_01/sud_vo_adv_bond_aoi_01_01-aoi002.m4a",
      "text": "ああ、新曲の振り付けで気になるところがあってね\n昼食後の腹ごなしだよ。ちょっと見ててくれない？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ahh‚ there's someting about new song's choreography that bothers me\nIt's exercising after lunch. Can you take a look at this?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 12.000000763,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolyard-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolyard-00-noon",
      "startTime": 20.0666674297
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_aoi_01_01/sud_vo_adv_bond_aoi_01_01-ai002.m4a",
      "text": "は、はい！　私で良ければ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "S-Sure! If it's okay with me",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 20.0666674297,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolyard-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolyard-00-noon",
      "startTime": 23.0666674297
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_aoi_01_01/sud_vo_adv_bond_aoi_01_01-aoi003.m4a",
      "text": "今の振り付けは、この後\nこんな感じでターンを一回入れるんだけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The choreography right now\nhas one turn like this‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 23.0666674297,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolyard-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolyard-00-noon",
      "startTime": 28.7666674297
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_aoi_01_01/sud_vo_adv_bond_aoi_01_01-aoi004.m4a",
      "text": "ちょっと地味なんだよね\nターンするなら二回は入れたい。ほら、こんな風に",
      "translations": {
        "en": "and it's a little simple\nIf I do a turn‚ I want to do it twice. Look‚ like this",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 28.7666674297,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolyard-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolyard-00-noon",
      "startTime": 31.53333
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolyard-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolyard-00-noon",
      "startTime": 35.7666674297
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_aoi_01_01/sud_vo_adv_bond_aoi_01_01-ai003.m4a",
      "text": "えぇ！？　あの短い間奏中に二回転ですか？\n葵さんはともかく、私に出来るかな……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What!? Two turns in that short time?\nAoi-san aside‚ I wonder if I can do it…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 35.7666674297,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolyard-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolyard-00-noon",
      "startTime": 44.1666687012
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_aoi_01_01/sud_vo_adv_bond_aoi_01_01-aoi005.m4a",
      "text": "愛なら出来るよ\n愛の身体能力は僕より上だと思うし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ai‚ you can do it\nI think Ai's physical abilities are higher than mine",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 44.1666687012,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolyard-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolyard-00-noon",
      "startTime": 49.4000020345
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_aoi_01_01/sud_vo_adv_bond_aoi_01_01-ai004.m4a",
      "text": "め、滅相もないです！　私はただのマッスルですから\nそれに、ダンスの才能には天と地ほどの差が……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "N-No way! I just have a lot of muscle\nBesides‚ there is a world of difference in dance talent…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 49.4000020345,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolyard-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolyard-00-noon",
      "startTime": 57.7000030518
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_aoi_01_01/sud_vo_adv_bond_aoi_01_01-aoi006.m4a",
      "text": "愛に才能がない訳ないじゃないか\n……そうだ、一緒に合わせてやってみよう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "There's no way Ai doesn't have talent\n…Yeah‚ let’s try that together",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 57.7000030518,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolyard-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolyard-00-noon",
      "startTime": 63.6000030518
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_aoi_01_01/sud_vo_adv_bond_aoi_01_01-ai005.m4a",
      "text": "え、えぇっ！？\n葵さんと、今からここでですか！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hu‚ huh!?\nWith Aoi-san‚ right here and now!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 63.6000030518,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolyard-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolyard-00-noon",
      "startTime": 67.9666742961
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_aoi_01_01/sud_vo_adv_bond_aoi_01_01-aoi007.m4a",
      "text": "他に誰と一緒にやるつもりなの？\nほら、僕の隣に来て。時間もないし、軽くだよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Who else are you going to do with?\nCome on‚ come next to me. We don't have much time‚ so let's take it easy",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 67.9666742961,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolyard-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolyard-00-noon",
      "startTime": 75.4666742961
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_aoi_01_01/sud_vo_adv_bond_aoi_01_01-ai006.m4a",
      "text": "わ、分かりました。どうかお手柔らかに……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "O-Okay. Please go easy on me…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 75.4666742961,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolyard-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolyard-00-noon",
      "startTime": 81.6614799499
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_aoi_01_01/sud_vo_adv_bond_aoi_01_01-aoi008.m4a",
      "text": "ほら、出来た。簡単だったでしょ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "See‚ that's it. Simple‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 82.9333414715,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolyard-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolyard-00-noon",
      "startTime": 85.3000050863
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_aoi_01_01/sud_vo_adv_bond_aoi_01_01-ai007.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ、はぁ、は、はひ、出来ましたけど……\nぜ、全然簡単では……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Haa‚ haa‚ ha‚ h-ha‚ I could have done it‚ but…\nI-It's not that simple at all…!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 85.3000050863,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolyard-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolyard-00-noon",
      "startTime": 94.9333429973
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_aoi_01_01/sud_vo_adv_bond_aoi_01_01-aoi009.m4a",
      "text": "それじゃ、せっかくだし\n忘れないように反復しよう。あと十回",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚ taking this opportunity‚\nlet's repeat it so we don't forget. 10 more times",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 94.9333429973,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolyard-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolyard-00-noon",
      "startTime": 99.8000096639
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_aoi_01_01/sud_vo_adv_bond_aoi_01_01-ai008.m4a",
      "text": "じゅっ、十回……！？\nさっき、軽くって言ったじゃないですか～！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "10‚ 10 times…!?\nI told you earlier to do it easy~!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 99.8000096639,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolyard-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolyard-00-noon",
      "startTime": 105.6000142415
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_aoi_01_01/sud_vo_adv_bond_aoi_01_01-aoi010.m4a",
      "text": "十回だよ？　軽いでしょ？　マッスルなんでしょ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's 10 times‚ right? It's easy‚ right? It's muscle‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 105.6000142415,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolyard-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolyard-00-noon",
