    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_aoi_01_01/sud_vo_adv_bond_aoi_01_01-ai009.m4a",
      "text": "マッスルは関係ないですよ！？\nそれに葵さんの軽くは、私にはすっごく重いんです！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Muscles have nothing to do with it!?\nBesides‚ Aoi-san's easy level is really difficult for me!",
